{"title":"“第一批伤亡”","authors":["天马","方成"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":3,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“第一批伤亡”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马诗　方成画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵越美海军陆战队胆小怕死，误向自己人开枪，三名美国兵中弹伤亡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海军陆战队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登陆在岘港，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表面很威风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里胆不壮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海风阵阵吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草木沙沙响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都疑有人来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担心把命丧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天还好过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚吓得慌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了防万一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巡逻又站岗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽听脚步声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乒乓就开枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把性命保，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先下手为强！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪法真是准，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战果太辉煌："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三人倒下地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一死两受伤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近前看一看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魂魄飞天上："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是自己人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一副凄惨相！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"误会呀误会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"懊丧呀懊丧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑话呀笑话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲伤呀悲伤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一批登陆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一批伤亡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南越游击队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未曾放一枪！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}